    • Field Detail

      • GET_AUTH_TOKEN_REQUEST

        protected static final String GET_AUTH_TOKEN_REQUEST
        The Cloud Shell back authorization channel uses serialized Javascript Protobufers, preceeded by the message length and a new line character. However, the request message has no content, so a token request consists of an empty JsPb, and its 2 character lenth prefix.

        Constant Field Values
